Class EventService

  • java.lang.Object
    • services.GenericService<EventRequest,​EventResponse>
      • services.EventService
  • public class EventService
extends GenericService<EventRequest,​EventResponse>
    This service provides functionality for the event getter endpoint. It accepts calls through the HTTP GET method.
